529, 119.9504, 120.8368, 121.9283, 122.6382, 122.3016, 121.626, 123.6268, 124.3727, 124.2632, 125.9842, 127.3034, 127.6037, 129.1043, 128.6505, 127.5152, 127.9018, 129.6588, 128.0069, 128.1139, 127.8751, 126.6186, 126.5284, 125.7038, 125.2837, 125.134, 125.7691, 124.7084, 125.1886, 125.583, 125.579, 125.0382, 124.9913, 125.0364, 124.8998, 124.6394, 124.1687, 124.3562, 124.4209, 123.7785, 124.041, 123.8341, 123.6632, 123.5258, 123.2237, 122.7633, 123.2629, 123.4787, 123.5052, 123.9098, 124.125, 122.9683, 123.0592, 123.9175, 122.5933, 121.9565, 121.2216, 121.5096, 121.7265, 121.7327, 122.0451, 121.2218, 120.9605, 121.0963, 120.6852, 120.4548, 120.485, 119.8079, 118.855, 118.7345, 118.3926, 118.3808, 118.7291, 119.6205, 120.3777, 119.6016, 120.8888, 121.4295, 122.4747, 123.0594, 121.549, 121.1121, 122.0074, 121.0992, 122.2652, 121.615, 121.8401, 122.2554, 122.792, 123.0992, 122.4509, 123.8877, 123.7998, 123.9205, 124.935, 126.5792, 126.9514, 126.9524, 127.6941, 126.7241, 124.6744, 124.8082, 124.3805, 124.2087, 123.83, 123.6721, 124.2673, 123.0175, 122.1634, 120.2981, 119.3392, 119.1926, 120.337, 121.4801, 120.7798, 120.9414, 121.1983, 121.3459, 120.4114, 120.399, 119.9323, 120.1278, 118.7802, 119.8644, 118.4781, 120.0512, 120.6731, 120.8019, 122.0985, 122.7997, 122.1765, 122.4718, 121.9667, 121.1793, 120.5732, 119.8906, 120.0491, 120.9706, 120.2293, 124.0998, 128.8795, 125.9651, 124.0711, 125.7467, 121.3742, 125.0852, 125.4774, 122.1852, 121.1629, 117.0593, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>机构持仓（三）：机构偏好与因子构建</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>原报告在 A 股上发现\"机构持仓<strong>变化率</strong>\"因子比\"持仓水平\"更有效（提前增加率累计 9×）。移植到商品期货：用 <code>memberdiff20</code> (Top-20 会员净持仓) 作为机构定向信号代理，计算多窗口（10/21/63 日）EMA 平滑后变化，截面等权 rank 合成，top 30% long / bottom 30% short，21 日 rebalance。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.53</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>2.5%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-11.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.58</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.08</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>-0.25 / 1.07</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.02</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.01</span></td><td>1.77</td><td>0.86</td><td>1.82</td><td>0.81</td><td>0.88</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.16</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.44</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>memberdiff20</code></td><td>席位净持仓差</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每日</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>38.4%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>30.1</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\tilde D_{t,i}=\\text{EMA}_{21}(\\text{memberdiff20}_{t,i}),\\quad \\Delta_w \\tilde D_{t,i}=\\tilde D_{t,i}-\\tilde D_{t-w,i}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">C_{t,i}=\\frac{1}{3}\\sum_{w\\in\\{10,21,63\\}}\\text{CSrank}_t(\\Delta_w\\tilde D_{t,i})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">s_{t,i}=\\begin{cases}+1&amp;C_{t,i}\\ge 0.7\\\\-1&amp;C_{t,i}\\le 0.3\\\\0&amp;\\text{else}\\end{cases},\\ w_{t,i}=s^{\\text{hold21}}_{t,i}/\\sum_j|s^{\\text{hold21}}_{t,j}|</div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p>R1 (0.751): 12 变体覆盖 level/change/combo 家族；Δmemberdiff20 21d 最优；Δmember_all 负；level-short 负。<strong>发现：方向信号的变化率是主 alpha 源，非水平</strong>。 R2 (<strong>0.966 ✓</strong>, +29%): 弃 memall-change 家族；加多窗口 combo；10/21/63 等权 rank 突破 0.8。多窗口合成平滑单窗口噪声，ts_icir 0.085→0.332，后半 Sharpe 1.59 vs 前半 0.31。 R3 (0.966 持平): 5 种窗口组合 + 动量 combo + hold/quantile 变动全部无改进；top 10 变体均 ≥0.85，稳健。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li>daily 频率，全商品 (~57 主力)</li>\n<li>21 日 rebalance，gross-exposure 归一化</li>\n<li>T+1 开盘成交，单边 4bps</li>\n<li>关键发现: 机构持仓<strong>变化率</strong> (Δmemberdiff20) &gt; 水平。对比机构持仓（十二）分域 (Sharpe 0.82): 本报告用变化率直接得 0.97，动量 combo 增益有限 — 说明 Δmdiff 已捕捉\"机构流-趋势\" 效应。</li>\n<li>局限: 与既有 huachuan_diff 因子 corr 0.41 非冗余但相关，2019 早期负贡献（品种池稀疏），后续年度稳定。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>INST_W</code></td><td><code>21</code></td><td>EMA span for memberdiff20</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9981</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.65s</li>\n</ul>"}